{"tid":1537371,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"對家武力現全係面升級，對策","createTime":"2019-09-04T01:58:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T03:11:15.000Z","uid":145768,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"70d60d3eb0ef66c2cf32aabc219fbd424d982e71","tid":1537371,"uid":145768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:58:11.000Z","msg":"眼見身邊一個又一個朋友發夢醒唔返，已經開始有小小無力感。<br />\n不過，係呢個時候大家都唔可以放棄，但有小小野想講：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">對家</span></span></strong><br />\n１.對方武力係８月下旬已經全面升級　如：<br />\ni)明目張膽地進入商場<br />\nii)行刑式使用槍械攻擊平民<br />\niii)非法進入私人地方/公共交通設施進行濫捕<br />\niv)使用槍械瞄準示威者要害攻勢<br />\nv)831<br />\nvi)攻擊記者<br />\n<br />\n以上都可以見到黑狗既武力以及做事手法已經更過份。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我地</span></strong></span><br />\n-依然用身體去擋子彈<br />\n-被動或被攻擊<br />\n-更多被捕<br />\n<br />\n所以，我地應該更有對策去應對班狗<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">發夢前</span>，應該做一個大召集，非當區，再一齊前住，盡量用大型運輸交通公具，人數要５０人以上，以免班狗昨日上巴士拘捕手足，最好用黨鐵，唔洗比錢又可以ｇｐ到好多人。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">發夢時</span></strong>昨日見到有手足開左個１５分鐘為限既ｐｏｓｔ，本人認為值得參考，以１５分鐘左上限，be water。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">夢醒</span>有兩個方法<br />\n１.大型集會可以家長接送點到點接送，事前要聯絡，ｔｇ有義載ｇｐ，或者相熟義載司機。<br />\n２.大型共公交通，如黨鐵（建議），巴士包車。因為巴士包車唔可以手足一齊走，黨鐘係有優勢，而黨鐵如果關站，可以以行街方式步行到其他站（不建議２個站以上）<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">必要時請棄裝</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">武力方面</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自己諗，人地呢加打你大力左，你仲要感化佢既都唔會有和平獎</span></span><br />\n尊重前線，有招請出扣，唔想見到身邊再有人比人拉<br />\n<br />\n利申：幫朋友出post　核爆都唔割"},{"pid":"f95a2a4d5c444f956a11baa08a7c01ee3aaca776","tid":1537371,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:58:28.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1f39ddde5919a42f493f808d799dbd534cf2302","tid":1537371,"uid":267425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:58:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>解散警隊 刻不容緩</strong></span></span><br />\n我屌曬你地老母快啲推第六大訴求<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536852</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fLDFcUN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfLDFcUN.jpg&h=350c6ca1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3935fb4741b8553b0e12a5e90830925d6c6ed8b","tid":1537371,"uid":145768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:58:45.000Z","msg":"自推01"},{"pid":"de9d90aa92e6dd4b66595a2505daa6af878d7815","tid":1537371,"uid":145768,"li